{
  "video_id": "t8R_GKS-M2Y",
  "title": "The future of good food in China | Matilda Ho",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12817.0,
      "end_time": 17150.0,
      "text": "I was six when I had the first chance to learn what patience means."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 18990.0,
      "end_time": 21461.0,
      "text": "My grandmother gave me a magic box as a birthday present,"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 21485.0,
      "end_time": 24770.0,
      "text": "which neither of us knew would become a gift for life."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 25817.0,
      "end_time": 28294.0,
      "text": "I became obsessed with magic,"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 28318.0,
      "end_time": 31889.0,
      "text": "and at 20, I became an amateur dove magician."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 33467.0,
      "end_time": 36594.0,
      "text": "This act of magic requires that I train my doves"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 36618.0,
      "end_time": 38839.0,
      "text": "to sit and wait inside my clothing."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 39738.0,
      "end_time": 44461.0,
      "text": "As a young magician, I was always in a rush to make them appear,"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 44485.0,
      "end_time": 46320.0,
      "text": "but my teacher told me"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 46560.0,
      "end_time": 49443.0,
      "text": "the secret to the success of this magical act"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 49468.0,
      "end_time": 53691.0,
      "text": "is to make my doves appear only after they&#39;ve waited patiently"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 53715.0,
      "end_time": 54948.0,
      "text": "in my tuxedo."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 55797.0,
      "end_time": 58817.0,
      "text": "It has to be a mindful kind of patience,"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 58841.0,
      "end_time": 61829.0,
      "text": "the kind that took me some years to master."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 63789.0,
      "end_time": 66904.0,
      "text": "When life took me to Shanghai seven years ago,"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 66928.0,
      "end_time": 71393.0,
      "text": "the mindful patience I learned became almost impossible to practice."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 72419.0,
      "end_time": 76387.0,
      "text": "In China, where everyone and everything is in a hurry,"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 76412.0,
      "end_time": 79864.0,
      "text": "you need to outperform over 1.3 billion other people"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 79888.0,
      "end_time": 81197.0,
      "text": "to build a better life."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 82601.0,
      "end_time": 85150.0,
      "text": "You hack the system, bend the rules,"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 85390.0,
      "end_time": 86546.0,
      "text": "circumvent the boundaries."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 87530.0,
      "end_time": 89561.0,
      "text": "It is the same when it comes to food ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 90500.0,
      "end_time": 93514.0,
      "text": "except that when it comes to food,"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 93538.0,
      "end_time": 96593.0,
      "text": "impatience can have dire consequences."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 97618.0,
      "end_time": 100357.0,
      "text": "In the haste to grow more, sell more,"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 100381.0,
      "end_time": 105364.0,
      "text": "4,000 years of agriculture in a country of rich natural resources"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 105388.0,
      "end_time": 108768.0,
      "text": "is spoiled by the overuse of chemicals and pesticides."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 109650.0,
      "end_time": 112603.0,
      "text": "In 2016, the Chinese government revealed"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 112627.0,
      "end_time": 116919.0,
      "text": "half a million food safety violations in just nine months."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 118125.0,
      "end_time": 121856.0,
      "text": "Alarmingly, one in every four diabetics in the world"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 121880.0,
      "end_time": 123426.0,
      "text": "now comes from China."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 124742.0,
      "end_time": 126455.0,
      "text": "The stories around food"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 126479.0,
      "end_time": 129941.0,
      "text": "are scary and somewhat overwhelming,"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 129965.0,
      "end_time": 135361.0,
      "text": "and I told myself it&#39;s time to bring a mindful patience into the impatience."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 136352.0,
      "end_time": 138170.0,
      "text": "When I say mindful patience,"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 138194.0,
      "end_time": 140201.0,
      "text": "I don&#39;t mean the ability to wait."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 140966.0,
      "end_time": 143799.0,
      "text": "I mean knowing how to act while waiting."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 145751.0,
      "end_time": 148336.0,
      "text": "And so, while I wait for the day"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 148360.0,
      "end_time": 152328.0,
      "text": "when a sustainable food system becomes a reality in China,"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 152352.0,
      "end_time": 155662.0,
      "text": "I launched one of China&#39;s first online farmers market"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 155686.0,
      "end_time": 159161.0,
      "text": "to bring local, organically grown produce to families."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 160488.0,
      "end_time": 162661.0,
      "text": "When we went live, 18 months ago,"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 162685.0,
      "end_time": 165273.0,
      "text": "the food we could sell then was somewhat dismal."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 166600.0,
      "end_time": 169460.0,
      "text": "We had no fruit and hardly any meat to sell,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 169700.0,
      "end_time": 173610.0,
      "text": "as none that was sent to the lab passed our zero tolerance test"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 173860.0,
      "end_time": 177880.0,
      "text": "towards pesticides, chemicals, antibiotics and hormones."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 177572.0,
      "end_time": 179668.0,
      "text": "I told our very anxious employees"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 179692.0,
      "end_time": 184144.0,
      "text": "that we would not give up until we&#39;ve met every local farmer in China."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 185882.0,
      "end_time": 189724.0,
      "text": "Today, we supply 240 types of produce"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 189748.0,
      "end_time": 191826.0,
      "text": "from 57 local farmers."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 192732.0,
      "end_time": 195306.0,
      "text": "After almost one year of searching,"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 195330.0,
      "end_time": 198177.0,
      "text": "we finally found chemical-free bananas"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 198201.0,
      "end_time": 201391.0,
      "text": "grown in the backyards of villagers on Hainan Island."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 202569.0,
      "end_time": 205351.0,
      "text": "And only two hours away from Shanghai,"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 205376.0,
      "end_time": 209447.0,
      "text": "on an island that even Google Maps does not have coordinates for,"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 209471.0,
      "end_time": 212241.0,
      "text": "we found a place where cows eat grass"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 212265.0,
      "end_time": 214430.0,
      "text": "and roam free under the blue sky."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 215941.0,
      "end_time": 218124.0,
      "text": "We also work hard on logistics."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 218690.0,
      "end_time": 222111.0,
      "text": "We deliver our customers&#39; orders in as fast as three hours"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 222135.0,
      "end_time": 224780.0,
      "text": "on electric vehicles,"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 224103.0,
      "end_time": 226802.0,
      "text": "and we use biodegradable, reusable boxes"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 226826.0,
      "end_time": 229380.0,
      "text": "to minimize our environmental footprint."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 230885.0,
      "end_time": 234917.0,
      "text": "I have no doubt that our offerings will continue to grow,"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 234941.0,
      "end_time": 236854.0,
      "text": "but it will take time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 236878.0,
      "end_time": 241472.0,
      "text": "and I know a lot more people are needed to shape the future of good food."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 242390.0,
      "end_time": 247858.0,
      "text": "So last year, I founded China&#39;s first food tech accelerator and VC platform"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 247883.0,
      "end_time": 250844.0,
      "text": "to help start-ups to shape the future of good food"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 250868.0,
      "end_time": 252430.0,
      "text": "the way they want,"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 252455.0,
      "end_time": 257400.0,
      "text": "be that through using edible insects as a more sustainable source of protein"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 257423.0,
      "end_time": 261176.0,
      "text": "or using essential oils to keep food fresh for longer."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 262514.0,
      "end_time": 264594.0,
      "text": "So, you may still ask:"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 264618.0,
      "end_time": 267935.0,
      "text": "Why are you trying to build a sustainable food system"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 267959.0,
      "end_time": 269942.0,
      "text": "by driving a patient movement"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 269966.0,
      "end_time": 273212.0,
      "text": "in a country where it&#39;s almost a crime to take it slow?"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 274329.0,
      "end_time": 275686.0,
      "text": "Because, for me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 275710.0,
      "end_time": 279265.0,
      "text": "the real secret to success is patience --"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 279290.0,
      "end_time": 281990.0,
      "text": "a mindful kind of patience"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 281123.0,
      "end_time": 284925.0,
      "text": "that requires knowing how to act while waiting,"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 284949.0,
      "end_time": 288668.0,
      "text": "the kind of patience I learned with my grandmother&#39;s magic box."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 289865.0,
      "end_time": 294460.0,
      "text": "After all, we do not inherit the earth from our ancestors."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 295300.0,
      "end_time": 297174.0,
      "text": "We borrow it from our children."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 297199.0,
      "end_time": 298350.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 298374.0,
      "end_time": 303230.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}